summary:
Always ready for amazing and exciting projects, at this moment I am part of an outstanding company that helps to build dreams based in a mix of passion, love and devotion for music.

I have been all my life interested in IT, but I cannot deny that music is something that moves people. Everybody loves and needs music and currently I am part of this world that I love. I am one of the main points of contact for dealers in Spain, Portugal or Andorra, back up for Italy when is necessary and Amazon Europe too. Even if I never studied Portuguese or Italian, I feel comfortable with those two languages and I hope at some time be able to be able to speak it and write it correctly, as I can understand great part of them.

I love to travel, to meet different countries, cultures and probably that helps me to stay comfortably in any country. Each year I try to visit at least a new country, discover new places, interact with local people... I am sure that is reflected in my daily work, where I find basic the connection with our clients and their satisfaction is my main goal, as that has an inmediate positive impact for our company and image. If we want to continue as the most important brand in the music industry, we need to offer something intangible with our products.

At the same time, I cannot conceive be working in a place where I am not happy. For me, it is an essential part, everything is important. The atmosphere, the colleagues, to believe in what I am doing... all helps to bring the 100%. 

I hope to keep growing and learning more and more about how to deal with any inconvenience, turn any negative experience in an unexpected opportunity to improve and create new opportunities.
